[Reports of neuraminidase-resistance have been rare overall, and as reported above, none from the European region this season. Overall the WHO global survey less optimistic than the European regional surrey in assessment of the current influenza situation, but it is clear that no new humans strains of enhanced pathogenicity have made an appearance this season in the northern hemisphere. - Mod.CP]
